						<div class="postbody">ABS,X and ABS,Y:<br />Treat address as two bytes High, Low.<br />Read from (High)×256 + ((Low + X)&amp;255).<br />Then if (Low+X) &gt; 256, read from (High+1)×256 + ((Low + X)&amp;255).</div>

